org.eclipse.eef

Interface EEFValidationRuleDescription

  • All Superinterfaces:
    org.eclipse.emf.ecore.EObject, org.eclipse.emf.common.notify.Notifier
    All Known Subinterfaces:
    EEFPropertyValidationRuleDescription, EEFSemanticValidationRuleDescription
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    EEFPropertyValidationRuleDescriptionImpl, EEFSemanticValidationRuleDescriptionImpl, EEFValidationRuleDescriptionImpl

    public interface EEFValidationRuleDescription
extends org.eclipse.emf.ecore.EObject
    A representation of the model object 'EEF Validation Rule Description'.

    The following features are supported:

    • Severity
    • Message Expression
    • Audits
    • Fixes
    See Also:
    EefPackage.getEEFValidationRuleDescription()
